    'NQT-0293', 'In a certain code language, if ''SPRING'' is encrypted as ''ZWYPUN'', how will ''SEEDS'' be written in that same cipher system?', NULL, '[{"id": "A", "text": "ZLLKZ"}, {"id": "B", "text": "AMMLA"}, {"id": "C", "text": "YKKJY"}, {"id": "D", "text": "BNNMB"}]'::jsonb, 'A', 
