I am writing to formally request the postponement of the system integration test because of unresolved bugs in the payment gateway code. This adjustment will ensure that our team has sufficient capacity to deliver high-quality results without compromising the project standards.

We appreciate your guidance and look forward to your approval of this request.

Best regards,
[Your Name]', 
    'Evaluate based on formal subject line, introduction stating request for the postponement of the system integration test, professional tone, and length.', NULL, 'Email Writing', 'Professional Communication', 
    'Medium'::nqt_difficulty, 'Verbal Ability'::nqt_section, 'Text'::nqt_question_type, 540, 
